{"tid":2338441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国網遊公司內鬥 董事長遭同事投毒 腦部受損","createTime":"2020-12-24T04:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T06:03:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"358d30cc5d616dfc71bb884ed72d1a08cb69a9b6","tid":2338441,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T04:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.worldjournal.com/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/wj/realtime/2020/12/24/9910303.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;q=75&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.worldjournal.com%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fwj%2Frealtime%2F2020%2F12%2F24%2F9910303.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26q%3D75%26nt%3D1&h=583d8bea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上市遊戲公司「遊族網絡」董事長林奇驚傳遭人投毒。（新華社）<br />\n<br />\n中國上市遊戲公司「遊族網絡」董事長林奇驚傳遭人投毒，投毒者還是公司前高層，犯案原因尚不清楚。中國《財新網》稱，林奇目前已無生命危險，但腦部受到不可逆損傷。<br />\n<br />\n上海市公安局官方微博23日晚間7點多發布訊息稱，本月17日17時許，警方接到報警稱，某醫院在診療時發現病患林某（男，39歲）疑似中毒。<br />\n<br />\n經現場勘查和調查走訪，警方發現林某的同事許某（男，39歲）有重大作案嫌疑。目前，許某已被警方依法刑事拘留，相關偵查工作正在進一步開展中。<br />\n<br />\n遊族網絡則於23日晚間8時發布聲明稱，遊族網絡董事長林奇16日晚返家途中出現急性不適症狀，隨即自行趕赴醫院。目前，治療方案和原因調查雙線都有明確進展，林奇正在住院恢復治療，各項體徵穩定。公司管理層已從上周的應急狀態中恢復，進入正常運轉。<br />\n<br />\n財新網引述業內人士說法指出，通報中的許某為許垚，系遊族網絡前高層，與林奇同樣是39歲，2017年5月起任職於遊族網絡，2018年2月至2019年1月期間擔任遊族網絡董事。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，2019年1月，許垚因個人原因申請離任董事，後轉往遊族旗下的遊族影業任職。<br />\n<br />\n遊族網絡創辦於2009年，於2014年借殼登陸A股，主營業務為手遊、頁遊的研發與運營。林奇是遊族網絡法定代表人、實際控制人、董事長兼總經理。截至今年第3季，林奇持股23.99%，為遊族網絡第一大股東。<br />\n<br />\n遊族的代表產品有《少年三國誌》、《盜墓筆記》、《權力的遊戲 凜冬將至》、《女神聯盟》等。遊族今年前三季，營收為人民幣37.24億元，增長40.95%；凈利5.60億元，下降20.56%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121474/5117871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2Fwj%2Fstory%2F121474%2F5117871&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=4f2f00af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121474/5117871</a>"},{"pid":"26d05c513fa980d8748131e580375da87e8a2eda","tid":2338441,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T04:26:59.000Z","msg":"本身個樣就似唐氏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717e78755e8b3b9dc22f8a90e13562acfcea84ca","tid":2338441,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T04:33:47.000Z","msg":"果然係中國人<br />\n最鐘意放毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f010d5a27b0a383c90a1d9a42a8a947547c289ad","tid":2338441,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T04:35:06.000Z","msg":"逼老闆給玩家送十連抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032eab2bdfeacdb87cfead1bc57baf8a685158bd","tid":2338441,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"717e78755e8b3b9dc22f8a90e13562acfcea84ca","tid":2338441,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T04:33:47.000Z","msg":"果然係中國人<br />\n最鐘意放毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T04:38:32.000Z","msg":"共產國家最中意落毒<br />\n<br />\n只求永久傷害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbe02963547befbfe6e4a72cbb2a4c07e1267f0","tid":2338441,"uid":42925,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T04:39:53.000Z","msg":"老闆說戰力最高送1個月獎金 我先來 我五星趙雲 戰力200萬"},{"pid":"28f96e7f014574317696dc1dd76b604f04960137","tid":2338441,"uid":12312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:01:21.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdd02004fafea34c727c5c3a443eaa04a4abe6d","tid":2338441,"uid":175208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:03:52.000Z","msg":"有抽魔關羽"},{"pid":"41c8e63eda4a91714ae90d803de552f45a404831","tid":2338441,"uid":175540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:05:41.000Z","msg":"變腦殘 幾有錢幾叻都冇用了"},{"pid":"17122726040eecff9a214bcb69dd0f2951d22929","tid":2338441,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf47b23aabafbb955e2cf73571e6af5b21bc80b0","tid":2338441,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />this is china"},{"pid":"a40cf35f5db4fa9b1fb748db759f48a1144a1bf1","tid":2338441,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:08:15.000Z","msg":"權力的遊戲"},{"pid":"703031d751623deca2795200d629f6ac2900996c","tid":2338441,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/991780/header.jpg?t=1606822015\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F991780%2Fheader.jpg%3Ft%3D1606822015&h=522f61b5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}